e.<br><br>Your information may be disclosed by you or at your direction, on blogs, forums, social media and other services to which you are able to post information and materials.  You should be aware that any information you disclose through these services will become public information, and may be available to the general public.  You authorize us to share your information with your social media account provider if you connect your use of our services to any of your social media accounts.<br><br>The basic, personally identifiable information that InJoy Global collects in order to perform and improve its services includes: names, birthdates, hire dates, employee number other employment information, usernames, mailing address, email address, phone number, height, weight and other information requested of participants of a contest.</div><br><br> 
